# Creative Gamemode Spawn Configuration

This file defines the spawn settings for Creative gamemode.

## Configuration Parameters
- `spawnPoint`: Coordinates of the spawn point.
- `spawnItems`: List of items to spawn at the beginning.

## Sample Settings
spawnPoint: {x: 100, y: 64, z: 100}
spawnItems:
  - Diamond
  - Gold Ingots
  - Potion of Speed
